data.description: Welcome to your dream home nestled in the charming Lake Port subdivision!     Located on a peaceful cul-de-sac, this home offers both tranquility and privacy. As you step through the elegant double foyer entrance, you'll be greeted by an abundance of natural light and an inviting atmosphere.    The heart of the home is the spacious living room, complete with a stunning double-sided fireplace, perfect for cozy evenings with loved ones. Adjacent to the living room is a delightful screened-in porch, where you can enjoy the serene views of the expansive, flat backyard – ideal for outdoor entertaining and recreation.    The oversized master bedroom is a true retreat, featuring ample space, a luxurious en-suite bathroom, and a walk-in closet. Additionally, the home offers generously sized spare rooms, providing plenty of space for guests, a home office, or a hobby room.    Convenience meets efficiency with the inclusion of an irrigation system, ensuring that your lawn stays lush and green year-round with minimal effort.    Meticulously maintained by its one owner, this home exudes pride of ownership and attention to detail at every turn. Don't miss your chance to make this exceptional property your own – schedule a showing today and prepare to fall in love!
